        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">Common Violations in San Jose</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class C (CO2) extinguishers in data center and server room environments — standard ABC dry chemical damages electronic equipment</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class K coverage in Japantown and Little Saigon restaurant commercial kitchens</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Expired annual tags in high-turnover tech company campus cafeteria and food service areas</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Inadequate coverage in biotech research lab spaces with flammable chemical storage</span></div></div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">San Jose Fire Prevention Contacts</h2>
